Subject: [PATCH v2 14/29] drm/radeon: Register ACPI video backlight when
 skipping radeon backlight registration
Date: Tue, 12 Jul 2022 21:38:55 +0200
Message-Id: <20220712193910.439171-15-hdegoede@redhat.com>
